[by:iRiemanr]
[00:57.23]I read your note, and I know just what you want to hear. 读你留的便签，心中明了你想要的回答
[01:10.26]It hurts less over time, but I’m not getting stronger. I just leave pieces behind. 时间能治愈伤痛，并不代表我会更坚强。我只留下回忆的碎片。
[01:21.77]And I can only fall so many times before I’m broke, unrecognizable. 等我多次落寞，物是人非之后，我只会更加堕落
[02:04.62]Now all I’ve left to give is the piece that still remains, and you bring the pieces back. 我留给你的那段时光依旧历历在目被你唤醒
[02:23.25]Love, it only reconstructs the pain. 所谓的爱情，只会唤起伤痛
[02:32.55]As time fails to elapse, I’m finding you were everything to me. 无法逃脱宿命，你是我的唯一
[02:46.06]Now my future and my past are ending tragically the same 但结局都一样  都是悲剧
